{
  "stem": "8423.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that if we blow up the tracks or anything like that, they'll find another way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyhow, the kids were really hoping and plotting that they were going to do something, in spite of it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six weeks, six weeks under these conditions in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they told us in the last minute, just before they were taking us, not to fret because they were just taking us to Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were going to work in factories, replacing the Germans who were in the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were taking their place and that we would be treated well, because we would be, you know, factory workers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my best friend Judy in the ghetto even said to me-- she came from Budapest and was a very sophisticated young woman, she went to one of these very advanced schools.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said to me, you know, that would be kind of fun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'll go to Germany and we'll perfect our German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we'll be treated like adults, because we'll be working in a factory rather than we're always treated like kids here, because we were too young to join the youth group, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she made it even sound like it was going to be a big adventure.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Judy Gerber, Judy Gerber.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Judy Gerber was one of these people who-- well, she was years ahead of me, even though she was only about six months older, because of her education and having grown up in a big city.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was-- she came from very liberal parents and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she really-- but unfortunately, no tradition in the home or anything, which I think finished her off in a way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because she had nothing to hold on to.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
